# Santa, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Santa () is a rural locality (a selo) in Shidibsky Selsoviet, Tlyaratinsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. The population was 44 as of 2010.
Geography
Santa is located 23&nbsp;km northwest of Tlyarata (the district's administrative centre) by road. Nukhotkolob is the nearest rural locality.
